Help put the fire out!

7
00:01:48,070 --> 00:01:48,630
The case files!

8
00:01:48,790 --> 00:01:49,990
Save the files!

9
00:01:50,630 --> 00:01:51,180
Hurry!

10
00:02:09,370 --> 00:02:09,830
[Episode 9]

11
00:02:09,830 --> 00:02:12,210
[Braving the Wind and Snow.
All for Some Fleeting Fame]

12
00:02:14,470 --> 00:02:17,380
Wu Ankang, Grand General
of the Left Imperial Guard,

13
00:02:17,950 --> 00:02:19,510
has long safeguarded the frontier,

14
00:02:20,260 --> 00:02:20,960
[Wu Ankang, Grand General]
repelling countless incursions

15
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:22,350
from the northern
and western barbarians,

16
00:02:23,030 --> 00:02:24,070
standing as a steadfast protector
of the realm.

17
00:02:24,310 --> 00:02:25,420
[Wu]
His hard work speaks volumes.

18
00:02:25,860 --> 00:02:26,910
In the second year of Shengxi,

19
00:02:27,540 --> 00:02:28,580
when the Shuodan forces
invaded our borders,

20
00:02:28,950 --> 00:02:30,660
[Dingding Gate]
General Wu led his army into battle,

21
00:02:30,820 --> 00:02:31,750
crushing the enemy in Mobei

22
00:02:32,100 --> 00:02:33,820
with overwhelming force

23
00:02:34,350 --> 00:02:36,630
and securing a decisive victory
in the Battle of Jinyuan.

24
00:02:37,030 --> 00:02:39,030
Now, as he returns in triumph,

25
00:02:39,910 --> 00:02:42,070
Her Majesty bestows upon him
the Azure Dragon Golden Mace

26
00:02:42,380 --> 00:02:43,470
and the Golden Radiant Armor.

27
00:02:43,950 --> 00:02:46,790
The Kangping Mansion is granted
a thousand liang of silver

28
00:02:47,030 --> 00:02:48,100
and five hundred pi of silk.

29
00:02:48,350 --> 00:02:50,630
Every soldier under his command
shall receive five pi of silk

30
00:02:50,790 --> 00:02:51,630
and ten thousand copper coins.

31
00:02:52,630 --> 00:02:53,790
Thus the imperial decree.

32
00:02:54,230 --> 00:02:55,910
Thank you, Your Majesty.

33
00:02:58,310 --> 00:02:59,100
General Wu,

34
00:02:59,910 --> 00:03:00,860
we convene today
to discuss state affairs.

35
00:03:01,190 --> 00:03:02,140
If you have any sound strategies,

36
00:03:02,470 --> 00:03:03,630
do not hesitate to share them.

37
00:03:04,100 --> 00:03:04,540
Yes, Your Majesty.

38
00:03:06,860 --> 00:03:08,790
Ministers, is there any matter
that requires my attention?

39
00:03:11,700 --> 00:03:12,700
I have an important issue
to bring to Your Majesty's attention.

40
00:03:13,190 --> 00:03:13,750
Go ahead.

41
00:03:14,470 --> 00:03:15,140
The Longmen Battle is a brutal show

42
00:03:15,350 --> 00:03:17,230
where lowborns kill each other
for the amusement of the spectators.

43
00:03:17,820 --> 00:03:19,420
For the sake of a mere document
freeing them from their lowly status,

44
00:03:20,070 --> 00:03:21,140
brothers turn against each other,

45
00:03:21,510 --> 00:03:22,380
families are torn apart,

46
00:03:23,070 --> 00:03:24,510
and countless lives are lost.

47
00:03:24,950 --> 00:03:26,140
Your Majesty, I earnestly implore you

48
00:03:26,700 --> 00:03:28,350
to issue a decree
to shut down Longmen Arena

49
00:03:28,700 --> 00:03:29,750
and abolish this inhumane practice.

50
00:03:29,980 --> 00:03:31,260
What baseless fearmongering!

51
00:03:31,660 --> 00:03:32,380
Longmen Arena

52
00:03:32,700 --> 00:03:33,860
has granted many lowborn individuals

53
00:03:34,070 --> 00:03:35,230
the chance to break free
from their status,

54
00:03:35,540 --> 00:03:36,380
and change their fate.

55
00:03:36,580 --> 00:03:37,540
This is clearly

56
00:03:37,860 --> 00:03:39,630
[Lu Qi, Minister of Works]
an act of great benevolence and grace,

57
00:03:39,950 --> 00:03:41,470
yet you slander it so.

58
00:03:42,030 --> 00:03:42,630
If I recall correctly,

59
00:03:42,910 --> 00:03:44,630
Mr. Yuan himself elevated his status

60
00:03:44,950 --> 00:03:45,750
through the Longmen Battle.

61
00:03:46,190 --> 00:03:46,750
What?

62
00:03:47,030 --> 00:03:48,350
You've benefited
from this policy yourself,

63
00:03:48,630 --> 00:03:49,630
but now you want to abolish it

64
00:03:49,980 --> 00:03:50,980
and prevent others
from having the same opportunity?

65
00:03:50,980 --> 00:03:52,790
[Zhang Quan, Minister of Justice]

66
00:03:52,790 --> 00:03:54,700
The Longmen Battle was personally
approved by Ruler Wen,

67
00:03:55,030 --> 00:03:56,790
yet Mr. Yuan branded it as flawed.

68
00:03:57,190 --> 00:03:59,030
Is he implying
that Ruler Wen is unjust?

69
00:03:59,660 --> 00:04:00,860
Such remarks by Mr. Yuan
betray malicious intent

70
00:04:01,310 --> 00:04:02,190
and cannot be overlooked!

71
00:04:02,980 --> 00:04:03,750
That is an unfair argument.

72
00:04:04,260 --> 00:04:05,190
The Longmen Battle was intended

73
00:04:05,470 --> 00:04:06,470
to provide the lowborn

74
00:04:06,510 --> 00:04:07,190
with a chance to change their fate.

75
00:04:07,510 --> 00:04:08,380
But it was limited

76
00:04:08,470 --> 00:04:09,700
to wrestling matches

77
00:04:09,910 --> 00:04:10,790
that avoided serious injury.

78
00:04:11,140 --> 00:04:12,070
[Xian Guangping]
Yet over time,

79
00:04:12,750 --> 00:04:14,100
[General of Left Yulin Royal Guard]
some have turned it

80
00:04:14,140 --> 00:04:15,750
into a bloodstained gambling den
where human lives are discarded at will.

81
00:04:16,310 --> 00:04:17,750
Mr. Yuan's claims are factual,

82
00:04:18,310 --> 00:04:20,140
yet you keep tying this matter
to Ruler Wen.

83
00:04:20,780 --> 00:04:21,460
Should we not question

84
00:04:21,820 --> 00:04:22,820
your intent behind such statements?

85
00:04:23,310 --> 00:04:24,070
How could this kind of contest

86
00:04:24,110 --> 00:04:25,380
be held without any injuries?

87
00:04:26,190 --> 00:04:27,460
Some with ulterior motives

88
00:04:27,580 --> 00:04:28,820
exaggerate the facts

89
00:04:28,870 --> 00:04:30,190
and now seek
to ruin a well-intended policy.

90
00:04:30,700 --> 00:04:31,670
Is that not laughable?

91
00:04:35,780 --> 00:04:36,700
Mr. Mei,

92
00:04:37,820 --> 00:04:38,700
what is your opinion?

93
00:04:39,900 --> 00:04:42,380
Each reign has its own ruler

94
00:04:42,550 --> 00:04:43,990
and its own system of governance.

95
00:04:45,140 --> 00:04:46,450
[Mei Bowen, Left Chancellor]
Since this policy

96
00:04:46,450 --> 00:04:47,430
has not yet been enshrined in law,

97
00:04:48,630 --> 00:04:49,700
whether it is altered or maintained

98
00:04:50,110 --> 00:04:51,550
is entirely up to Your Majesty.

99
00:04:52,020 --> 00:04:54,460
Previously, Minister Lu
and Minister Zhang

100
00:04:54,630 --> 00:04:56,070
often had significant disagreements.

101
00:04:56,110 --> 00:04:56,750
Today, however,

102
00:04:57,340 --> 00:04:58,430
they are in rare agreement.

103
00:04:58,820 --> 00:04:59,750
A chance to change their fate.

104
00:05:00,110 --> 00:05:02,220
I think what you've said is spot on.

105
00:05:02,750 --> 00:05:04,020
Does anyone else share the same view?

106
00:05:06,950 --> 00:05:08,460
- I do.
- I do.

107
00:05:11,780 --> 00:05:12,460
Someone,

108
00:05:13,430 --> 00:05:14,070
bring it up.

109
00:05:23,510 --> 00:05:24,310
Since this policy

110
00:05:24,670 --> 00:05:25,900
is so great,

111
00:05:26,750 --> 00:05:28,070
I will put it to the test myself.

112
00:05:28,900 --> 00:05:29,670
You two,

113
00:05:30,220 --> 00:05:31,550
in front of the ministers,

114
00:05:31,950 --> 00:05:32,900
will fight here

115
00:05:32,950 --> 00:05:34,020
in this cage.

116
00:05:34,870 --> 00:05:35,630
The winner

117
00:05:36,260 --> 00:05:36,870
will be awarded

118
00:05:37,380 --> 00:05:39,070
the position of Right Chancellor.

119
00:05:39,580 --> 00:05:40,220
How does that sound?

120
00:05:40,750 --> 00:05:42,140
- Your Majesty, please calm your anger.
- Your Majesty, please calm your anger.

121
00:05:42,310 --> 00:05:44,260
Why all the fuss about Yanqing Lane
being ominous?

122
00:05:44,990 --> 00:05:47,070
Why are so many of you
asking me not to go?

123
00:05:47,750 --> 00:05:49,220
What are you really afraid of?

124
00:05:51,630 --> 00:05:52,260
Minister Cui,

125
00:05:52,950 --> 00:05:54,260
did you enjoy

126
00:05:54,870 --> 00:05:55,820
the Longmen Battle yesterday?

127
00:05:56,070 --> 00:05:57,920
[Cui Yi, Vice Minister of Justice]

128
00:05:58,670 --> 00:05:59,510
Back in the day,

129
00:06:00,190 --> 00:06:00,820
there were those who deceived

130
00:06:00,820 --> 00:06:01,820
both their superiors
and their subordinates.

131
00:06:02,220 --> 00:06:02,950
Now,

132
00:06:03,340 --> 00:06:05,260
some still dare to use Ruler Wen's name
to justify their actions.

133
00:06:05,950 --> 00:06:07,870
All beings deserve to be treated
with compassion.

134
00:06:08,020 --> 00:06:09,550
Despite the gruesome nature
of the bloodshed,

135
00:06:09,870 --> 00:06:11,070
many noblemen

136
00:06:11,220 --> 00:06:12,380
eagerly flocked to the scene.

137
00:06:12,700 --> 00:06:13,900
What lies beneath their masks,

138
00:06:15,110 --> 00:06:16,670
man or demon?

139
00:06:17,580 --> 00:06:19,340
- Your Majesty, please calm your anger.
- Your Majesty, please calm your anger.

140
00:06:19,870 --> 00:06:21,670
Since I ascended the throne,

141
00:06:22,110 --> 00:06:22,700
I've decreed

142
00:06:22,820 --> 00:06:23,990
lighter taxes

143
00:06:24,310 --> 00:06:25,220
and returned wealth to the people.

144
00:06:25,670 --> 00:06:27,110
Yet, there are still areas

145
00:06:27,430 --> 00:06:28,550
plagued by refugees and fugitives.

146
00:06:29,380 --> 00:06:30,900
The barbarians eye our borders,

147
00:06:31,340 --> 00:06:33,110
and though I intended
to allocate funds for the military,

148
00:06:33,340 --> 00:06:35,110
I discovered a deficit
in the national treasury.

149
00:06:35,460 --> 00:06:37,820
Every matter I just mentioned,
big or small, is a national concern.

150
00:06:38,700 --> 00:06:39,700
Some individuals,

151
00:06:39,750 --> 00:06:41,070
living off their family's past merits,

152
00:06:41,110 --> 00:06:41,900
occupy their positions
without fulfilling their duties.

153
00:06:42,260 --> 00:06:44,190
Instead of focusing
on the well-being of the nation,

154
00:06:44,510 --> 00:06:45,820
they are obsessed
with preserving Longmen Arena,

155
00:06:45,870 --> 00:06:47,870
a place that treats human lives
as entertainment,

156
00:06:48,070 --> 00:06:49,430
nitpicking over petty details.

157
00:06:51,580 --> 00:06:52,110
Cui Yi.

158
00:06:54,900 --> 00:06:55,380
Yes, Your Majesty.

159
00:06:55,750 --> 00:06:57,550
As the Vice Minister of Justice,

160
00:06:58,110 --> 00:06:59,470
even before Minister Ji
arrived in the capital,

161
00:06:59,470 --> 00:07:00,190
it was already uncovered

162
00:07:00,220 --> 00:07:01,870
that you allowed your followers
to seize people's land

163
00:07:02,020 --> 00:07:03,670
and engage in corruption.

164
00:07:05,630 --> 00:07:07,110
Are you deserving

165
00:07:08,020 --> 00:07:09,820
of this official regalia?

166
00:07:11,190 --> 00:07:12,110
I am deeply ashamed for betraying
Your Majesty's trust.

167
00:07:12,310 --> 00:07:13,070
No punishment
could ever atone for my sins.

168
00:07:13,380 --> 00:07:13,990
I implore Your Majesty

169
00:07:14,510 --> 00:07:15,670
not to let my transgressions

170
00:07:15,820 --> 00:07:16,550
affect your well-being.

171
00:07:17,140 --> 00:07:17,750
Your Majesty.

172
00:07:18,110 --> 00:07:18,580
Your Majesty!

173
00:07:18,630 --> 00:07:19,550
By imperial decree,

174
00:07:20,220 --> 00:07:21,190
from this day forward,

175
00:07:21,630 --> 00:07:22,670
no one

176
00:07:23,190 --> 00:07:24,630
is to use coercion, bribery,
or any other means

177
00:07:24,750 --> 00:07:25,870
to force commoners to fight each other.

178
00:07:26,780 --> 00:07:27,630
Anyone who defies this order

179
00:07:28,140 --> 00:07:29,110
will receive eighty strokes

180
00:07:29,260 --> 00:07:30,580
and be exiled three thousand li away.

181
00:07:36,310 --> 00:07:36,950
Your Majesty,

182
00:07:37,780 --> 00:07:39,580
many have been placed in the lower ranks

183
00:07:39,700 --> 00:07:40,510
due to the mistakes of their ancestors,

184
00:07:40,950 --> 00:07:42,340
even though they themselves
are blameless.

185
00:07:43,190 --> 00:07:44,260
I humbly request that,

186
00:07:44,580 --> 00:07:46,110
those with two generations
or more in the lower class

187
00:07:46,340 --> 00:07:47,430
should be allowed

188
00:07:47,630 --> 00:07:48,550
to compete in scholarships,

189
00:07:49,220 --> 00:07:49,900
and those who excel be granted

190
00:07:50,460 --> 00:07:51,550
freedom from their low status.

191
00:07:51,550 --> 00:07:52,580
[Li Muyuan, Vice Minister]

192
00:07:52,580 --> 00:07:53,700
[of the Department of State Affairs]
It is out of the question.

193
00:07:55,070 --> 00:07:55,950
The imperial exams

194
00:07:56,260 --> 00:07:57,220
offer virtuous citizens

195
00:07:57,260 --> 00:07:58,750
the chance to serve the nation.

196
00:07:59,020 --> 00:08:00,780
It is inconceivable to extend
this opportunity to the low-born.

197
00:08:01,190 --> 00:08:01,780
If that happens,

198
00:08:01,900 --> 00:08:02,870
class distinctions will cease to exist,

199
00:08:03,220 --> 00:08:05,260
and the entire imperial system
will crumble,

200
00:08:05,580 --> 00:08:06,750
destabilizing
the very foundation of the state.

201
00:08:07,460 --> 00:08:08,820
Mr. Li makes a valid point.

202
00:08:09,310 --> 00:08:11,630
While Mr. Yuan's concern
for the people is commendable,

203
00:08:11,990 --> 00:08:14,670
such reforms may be too extreme

204
00:08:16,780 --> 00:08:18,780
and counterproductive.

205
00:08:20,380 --> 00:08:21,140
Mr. Mei,

206
00:08:21,380 --> 00:08:22,020
Mr. Li,

207
00:08:22,430 --> 00:08:23,510
you two are right.

208
00:08:24,070 --> 00:08:25,670
There's no need
to discuss this matter further.

209
00:08:26,190 --> 00:08:26,870
Minister Yuan,

210
00:08:27,510 --> 00:08:28,260
please rise.

211
00:08:28,990 --> 00:08:29,550
Yes, Your Majesty.

212
00:08:35,820 --> 00:08:36,390
Your Majesty,

213
00:08:37,580 --> 00:08:38,430
I have an idea

214
00:08:38,790 --> 00:08:39,500
regarding Longmen Arena.

215
00:08:40,100 --> 00:08:41,030
But I am not sure if it is feasible.

216
00:08:41,740 --> 00:08:42,740
Do tell.

217
00:08:43,430 --> 00:08:45,030
Whether a sword is used to inflict harm

218
00:08:45,150 --> 00:08:45,790
or provide salvation

219
00:08:46,620 --> 00:08:47,860
depends on the one who wields it.

220
00:08:48,430 --> 00:08:49,670
Treating the lives of the lower class
as a form of entertainment

221
00:08:50,070 --> 00:08:50,790
is a sin.

222
00:08:51,070 --> 00:08:51,820
But Longmen Arena itself

223
00:08:52,340 --> 00:08:53,500
bears no fault.

224
00:08:54,460 --> 00:08:56,430
It was built
under Ruler Wen's personal decree.

225
00:08:57,150 --> 00:08:58,270
To seal it off and abandon it

226
00:08:58,310 --> 00:08:59,070
would be a great loss.

227
00:09:00,340 --> 00:09:00,950
I propose

228
00:09:01,430 --> 00:09:02,190
that we allow

229
00:09:02,430 --> 00:09:03,550
skilled martial artists
to compete there,

230
00:09:04,030 --> 00:09:05,910
using it as a platform
to discover and promote talent.

231
00:09:10,620 --> 00:09:13,030
You truly are a seasoned general.

232
00:09:14,270 --> 00:09:15,460
Your proposal

233
00:09:15,580 --> 00:09:18,310
aligns perfectly with my idea
of establishing

234
00:09:18,790 --> 00:09:19,700
a military examination system.

235
00:09:20,310 --> 00:09:21,150
In that case,

236
00:09:21,500 --> 00:09:22,860
let's use Longmen Arena

237
00:09:23,070 --> 00:09:24,030
as a trial run.

238
00:09:24,670 --> 00:09:25,340
Issue a decree

239
00:09:26,500 --> 00:09:28,740
to change Longmen Arena
to a Martial Arts Examination Ground,

240
00:09:29,220 --> 00:09:30,430
with two officials
assigned to oversee it.

241
00:09:31,100 --> 00:09:31,950
Those who stand out

242
00:09:32,430 --> 00:09:34,980
will be included
in the military officer selection list

243
00:09:35,460 --> 00:09:36,500
for further evaluation.

244
00:09:37,860 --> 00:09:39,790
- Your Majesty is wise.
- Your Majesty is wise.

245
00:09:47,500 --> 00:09:49,030
Her Majesty went to Longmen Arena,

246
00:09:49,310 --> 00:09:50,670
and you did Yuan Shaocheng
a great favor.

247
00:09:51,550 --> 00:09:52,820
He surely owes you a proper thanks.

248
00:09:56,580 --> 00:09:57,220
What's wrong?

249
00:09:58,460 --> 00:09:58,980
Are you hurt?

250
00:09:59,220 --> 00:09:59,770
Let me take a look.

251
00:10:00,010 --> 00:10:00,700
I'm all right.

252
00:10:01,340 --> 00:10:02,300
I used too much force

253
00:10:02,420 --> 00:10:03,300
and strained my wrist.

254
00:10:03,530 --> 00:10:04,850
Why were you so dramatic then?

255
00:10:05,100 --> 00:10:06,060
You scared me half to death.

256
00:10:06,770 --> 00:10:07,850
It's just a sprained wrist,

257
00:10:07,890 --> 00:10:08,770
yet you screamed so loud.

258
00:10:09,460 --> 00:10:10,650
You really can't handle pain, can you?

259
00:10:12,420 --> 00:10:13,180
Now that I think about it,

260
00:10:14,130 --> 00:10:15,370
I have no idea how a certain someone

261
00:10:15,420 --> 00:10:16,250
managed to survive in prison.

262
00:10:16,820 --> 00:10:17,530
If it were me,

263
00:10:17,850 --> 00:10:18,820
I would have confessed
everything right away.

264
00:10:20,420 --> 00:10:21,130
Did you hear that?

265
00:10:21,580 --> 00:10:22,890
Don't put Cailian in charge.

266
00:10:23,420 --> 00:10:24,250
She'll spill everything

267
00:10:24,980 --> 00:10:26,130
the moment she's tortured.

268
00:10:26,610 --> 00:10:27,650
What do you mean?

269
00:10:33,980 --> 00:10:34,580
Cailian,

270
00:10:35,580 --> 00:10:36,010
is something

271
00:10:36,060 --> 00:10:36,890
on your mind lately?

272
00:10:39,890 --> 00:10:41,610
Let us know if anything's bothering you.

273
00:10:42,010 --> 00:10:42,460
No.

274
00:10:45,490 --> 00:10:47,730
If you don't tell me, I'll just guess.

275
00:10:49,060 --> 00:10:50,490
